comment: Grant (OKC) makes incidental contact with Ross (ORL) off ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Vucevic (ORL) moves his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Roberson (OKC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Vucevic (ORL) that does not affect his post move and shot attempt.
Gordon (ORL) legally contests Westbrook's (OKC) jump shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) firms up his position and sets the screen on Grant (OKC).
Adams (OKC) makes marginal contact with Payton (ORL) following the screen.
Adams (OKC) and Vucevic (ORL) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Adams (OKC) makes incidental contact with Vucevic (ORL) during the loose ball.
Vucevic (ORL) firms up his position and sets the screen on Oladipo (OKC).
Roberson (OKC) makes incidental contact with Fournier (ORL) that does not affect his SQBR.
Oladipo (ORL) makes contact to Fournier's (ORL) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Adams (OKC) makes incidental contact with Vucevic (ORL) that does not affect his rebound and shot attempt.
LO SLA shows Westbrook (OKC) clamp and pull Vucevic's (ORL) right arm, affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Gordon (ORL) legally contests Westbrook's (OKC) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Roberson (OKC) commits a take foul on Vucevic (ORL).
Vucevic (ORL) obtains a legal guarding position and jumps vertically contesting Westbrook's (OKC) driving shot attempt.
Adams (OKC) makes marginal contact with Ross (ORL), who initiates the contact.
[Incidental or immaterial] Roberson (OKC) makes contact with Fournier (ORL) that affects his FOM.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of OKC possession is overturned to an inadvertent whistle and ORL is awarded possession.
Grant (OKC) commits a take foul on Vucevic (ORL).
[Incidental or immaterial] Adams (OKC) grabs Gordon's (ORL) jersey during the rebound.
Payton (ORL) legally contests Westbrook's (OKC) jump shot attempt.
Fournier (ORL) avoids dislodging Abrines (OKC) from his legal guarding position and the contact is incidental.
McDermott (OKC) makes marginal contact with Vucevic (ORL) that does not affect his ability to control the pass.
